{{year-header}}
==February==
* '''[[14 February|14]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] dictates [[Letter to Arthur Tolkien|a letter to his father]].
* '''[[14 February|14]]''' - [[E.V. Gordon]], a later colleague of Tolkien, is born.
* '''[[15 February|15]]''' - [[Arthur Tolkien]] dies in [[Bloemfontein]], as a result of a severe hemorrhage suffered the previous day. He had been sick for many months with rheumatic fever, and never made the trip to [[Birmingham]] to see his family.
* '''?''' - [[Mabel Suffield|Mabel Tolkien]] and her family move from Birmingham to the hamlet of [[Sarehole]].

==April==

* '''[[7 April|7]]''' - [[Hugo Dyson]], [[Inklings|Inkling]], is born.

==August==
* '''[[1 August|1]]''' - [[John Benjamin Tolkien]], grandfather of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]], dies.
==October==
* '''[[3 October|3]]''' - [[William Morris]], artist and author who influenced [[J.R.R. Tolkien]], dies.
==?==
* '''?''' - [[James Dundas-Grant]], [[Inklings|Inkling]], is born.
